OL,5,G2000 Dom Chinea's Cornish Workshop
OL,6,     FCornish newcomer Dom Chinea tries
OL,7,     Fto fix a leaky sea pool near
OL,8,     FMousehole. He buys a battered old
OL,9,     FLand Rover and starts a new
OL,10,     Fproject crushing waste concrete to
OL,11,     Ffill potholes on his lane.
OL,12,G2100 Dom Chinea's Cornish Workshop
OL,13,     FDom tries out water dowsing so he
OL,14,     Fcan fill his new pond. He and
OL,15,     Fengineer friend Sam Lovegrove fix
OL,16,     Fsome church bells and then put a
OL,17,     Fsurf lifesaving club's quad bike
OL,18,     Fback on the beach.
