OL,5,G2320 Nurses on the Ward
OL,6,     FCaroline treats an unvaccinated
OL,7,     FCovid patient who's been in a coma
OL,8,     Ffor weeks. Matron Hazera assesses
OL,9,     Fa deep tissue injury and Kat cares
OL,10,     Ffor a man in pain after kidney
OL,11,     Fstone surgery.
OL,12,G0020 Nurses on the Ward
OL,13,     FMatron Hazera is called to save a
OL,14,     Fperson standing on the edge of a
OL,15,     Fbuilding, while nurse Kat treats a
OL,16,     Fwoman with suspected ovarian
OL,17,     Fcancer.
